(13, '1', '{\"success-story0\":{\"title\":\"Bhashini helps Vijay save a life\",\"text\":\"When Vijay\\u2019s friend Raju was pulled out of a well he was drowning in, he wasn\\u2019t breathing. Vijay had seen CPR in a video, but needed to know the exact procedure. \\r\\nThanks to Bhashini, Vijay was able to access the exact procedure in his local language, the only one that he could read at that tense moment. \",\"image\":\"images\\/success-stories\\/man1-img.png\"},\"success-story1\":{\"title\":\"Bhashini satisfies Mona\\u2019s curiosity\",\"text\":\"The brightest student in her village, 8 year old Mona wanted to become a scientist. Her curiosity for science and astronomy knew no bounds.  Thanks to Bhashini, Mona could access a huge library of books from across the country in her local language and dialect, making her even more curious about the world!\",\"image\":\"images\\/success-stories\\/user2-img.png\"},\"success-story2\":{\"title\":\"Bhashini generates income for Khurshid\",\"text\":\"The stock market always attracted Khurshid. On his shop counter, he had heard many customers talking about investing and that piqued his interest. \\r\\nThanks to Bhashini, Khurshid is now able to follow all the latest news, price movements and analysis in his mother tongue, bringing vital information to him and helping him invest.\",\"image\":\"images\\/success-stories\\/user3-img.png\"}}'),
