(225, 396, 'Footer Support Info - Malayalam', '', '<p>ഈ സൈറ്റ് ലഭിക്കുന്നതിന് ജാവാസ്ക്രിപ്റ്റ് പ്രയോഗ്യമാക്കിയിരിക്കണം</p>\r\n<p>പിൻതാങ്ങുന്നത്: ഫയർഫോക്സ്, ഗൂഗിൾക്രോം, ഇന്റർനെറ്റ് എക്സ്പ്ലോറർ 10.0+, സഫാരി</p>', 1, 'pages-footer-supportinfo', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{\"prepare_content\":0,\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\" footer-links\",\"cache\":1,\"cache_time\":900,\"cachemode\":\"static\",\"module_tag\":\"div\",\"bootstrap_size\":\"0\",\"header_tag\":\"h3\",\"header_class\":\"\",\"style\":\"0\"}', 0, 'ml-IN'),
(226, 397, 'Footer Support Info - Tamil', '', '<p>தளத்தை அணுக ஜாவாஸ்கிரிப்ட் இயக்கப்பட வேண்டும்.</p>\r\n<p>ஆதரிக்கிறது: பயர்பாக்ஸ், கூகுள் குரோம், இன்டர்நெட் எக்ஸ்ப்ளோரர் 10.0+, சபாரி</p>', 1, 'pages-footer-supportinfo', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{\"prepare_content\":0,\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\" footer-links\",\"cache\":1,\"cache_time\":900,\"cachemode\":\"static\",\"module_tag\":\"div\",\"bootstrap_size\":\"0\",\"header_tag\":\"h3\",\"header_class\":\"\",\"style\":\"0\"}', 0, 'ta-IN'),
(227, 398, 'Footer Support Info - Telugu', '', '<p>సైట్‌ను యాక్సెస్ చేయడానికి జావాస్క్రిప్ట్ ని తప్పనిసరిగా ప్రారంభించాలి.</p>\r\n<p>మద్దతుని అందించేవారు: ఫైర్‌ఫాక్స్, గూగుల్ క్రోమ్, ఇంటర్నెట్ ఎక్స్‌ప్లోరర్ 10.0+, సఫారి</p>', 1, 'pages-footer-supportinfo', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{\"prepare_content\":0,\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\" footer-links\",\"cache\":1,\"cache_time\":900,\"cachemode\":\"static\",\"module_tag\":\"div\",\"bootstrap_size\":\"0\",\"header_tag\":\"h3\",\"header_class\":\"\",\"style\":\"0\"}', 0, 'tl-IN'),
(228, 399, 'Footer Support Info - Punjabi', '', '<p>ਇਸ ਸਾਈਟ ਨੂੰ ਐਕਸੈਸ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਜਾਵਾ ਸਕ੍ਰਿਪਟ ਸਮਰੱਥ ਹੋਣਾ ਚਾਹੀਦਾ ਹੈ। ਸਮਰਥਨ ਕਰਦਾ ਹੈ:</p>\r\n<p>ਫਾਇਰਫੋਕਸ, ਗੂਗਲ ਕ੍ਰੋਮ, ਇੰਟਰਨੈੱਟ ਐਕਸਪਲੋਰਰ 10.0+, ਸਫਾਰੀ</p>', 1, 'pages-footer-supportinfo', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{\"prepare_content\":0,\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\" footer-links\",\"cache\":1,\"cache_time\":900,\"cachemode\":\"static\",\"module_tag\":\"div\",\"bootstrap_size\":\"0\",\"header_tag\":\"h3\",\"header_class\":\"\",\"style\":\"0\"}', 0, 'pb-IN'),
(229, 400, 'Footer Support Info - Odia', '', '<p>ସାଇଟକୁ ଏକସେସ କରିବା ପାଇଁ ଜାଭା ସ୍କ୍ରିପ୍ଟକୁ ସକ୍ରିୟ କରାନ୍ତୁ</p>\r\n<p>ସପୋର୍ଟ : ଫାୟାରଫକ୍ସ, ଗୁଗଲ କ୍ରୋମ, ଇଣ୍ଟରନେଟ ଏକ୍ସପଲୋରର 10.0+, ସଫାରୀ</p>', 1, 'pages-footer-supportinfo', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{\"prepare_content\":0,\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\" footer-links\",\"cache\":1,\"cache_time\":900,\"cachemode\":\"static\",\"module_tag\":\"div\",\"bootstrap_size\":\"0\",\"header_tag\":\"h3\",\"header_class\":\"\",\"style\":\"0\"}', 0, 'od-IN'),
